Lab: Ticketing system Solved

Scenario 
A user reported they cannot access the finance department shared drive via a ticket

Process:
I created a user and set their ticket to high priority due to it being part of the finance department
I then using the command prompt to troubleshoot the problem by first ping google.com it failed so i restarted the DHCP client service to now obtained a valid IP address
Connection was restored thereafter

Tools I used: spicework

